      <div type="section" xml:id="SID001">
        <head>de arte metrica</head>
        <p>Metrum phalaecium pedibus his constat: spondeo, dactylo, tribus trocheis.</p>
        <p>Metrum asclepiadeum his pedibus constat: spondeo, dactylo, dactylo, spondeo.</p>
